<plot>Ryan is ordered to a decrepit industry shop, where Blake, the leader of the gang he's involved in, reveals a figure sitting tied to a chair. It's Ryan's mother. Ryan is forced to prove his loyalty to Blake, by making a choice: Ryan must shoot his mother, or be shot himself. Fighting through Blake's quiet manipulation, Ryan revisits moments from his past that ultimately help him make up his mind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?115679</url></doc>
